{"tid":1377723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新作戰！！好嗎 （同意就推一推）","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:41:57.000Z","uid":208052,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"153c4ccc52f524fce29fdf0504104bf8d883dcea","tid":1377723,"uid":208052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"對唔住！咁多位，我八九點就走左番屋企，希望大家安全，香港加油！<br />\n<br />\n每一次發夢爬山，都會有兄弟犧牲。<br />\n我想提議一個全新作戰場地。<br />\n<br />\n現時作戰場地：市區<br />\n1. 一入夜，惡狗橫行<br />\n2. 影響社會不太<br />\n3. 兄弟受傷<br />\n4. ETC...<br />\n<br />\n新作戰場地：香港國際機場<br />\n1. 不夜城<br />\n2. 影響香港及國際<br />\n3. 惡狗一圍機場射槍，國際機場就拜拜了<br />\n<br />\n弊端<br />\n1. 出入不方便<br />\n<br />\n建議機場行動行先，狂搞，直接將機場搞到沉晒。希望有兄弟接受同諗下活動方向。"},{"pid":"e17254b860b1b7850025ab62806a88baf552094f","tid":1377723,"uid":208052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a33e3e31d54a1838acb102c05521bdbce354927","tid":1377723,"uid":208052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d217e600d82a986746840a7f6fb4118027a80b80","tid":1377723,"uid":277358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"惡狗唔一定要用槍架"},{"pid":"cfb3ea1edbf94814f5a413971c83692418ecc382","tid":1377723,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:32:18.000Z","msg":"同意，黑警如果機場放煙亂打人，國際機場之名就玩完，可以話係最安全地方"},{"pid":"576baeac7d1c6d4c0c3390e726f26dfa88b93eb4","tid":1377723,"uid":208052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d217e600d82a986746840a7f6fb4118027a80b80","tid":1377723,"uid":277358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"惡狗唔一定要用槍架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:32:55.000Z","msg":"惡狗入黎用棍打，香港機場都收得皮"},{"pid":"6dec25924648e56f37f9b618b5755d576b4d0338","tid":1377723,"uid":208052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid